&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The opportunity to have a significant impact on your team and the business in the work that you do&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Preparation and execution of all event catering relative to food and beverage (who doesn’t love a smoothie right?)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maintain full knowledge of menus, recipes, and other specification information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Participate in company-wide cost savings initiatives&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cooperate with implementation of cooperative training programs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Display passion for increasing knowledge of the culinary field through collaborative development and curation of menus and specials&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsible for constant sanitation, kitchen organisation, food handling and cleanliness&lt;/p&gt;
