&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;House Director&amp;nbsp; | NeueHouse Madison Square, NYC&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Convene Hospitality Group is seeking a visionary House Director (Director of Operations) to lead the ongoing operations and cultural evolution of our NeueHouse Madison Square location. As the strategic and operational leader of this iconic space and brand, you are responsible for the holistic success of the ‘House’, encompassing commercial and operational ownership, P&amp;amp;L accountability, member and guest experience, creative programming, and physical asset management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will provide executive oversight to our entire multidisciplinary team encompassing Membership &amp;amp; Sales, Membership Experience, Workplace Operations, Events, Food &amp;amp; Beverage, AV Production, and Facilities, ensuring the seamless execution of all programs, services, and experiences with the precision and hospitality synonymous with the NeueHouse brand. Reporting to Convene Hospitality Group Leadership, you will drive integrated business performance and operational excellence by leading high-impact cross-functional initiatives, while delivering elevated hospitality and cultivating a trendsetting brand that defines the global standard for creative community building.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity to be a founding pillar of a brand evolution. You will lead the charge in creating an environment where world class hospitality meets cultural innovation. You are the custodian of an iconic landmark, transforming it into a living, breathing ecosystem where influential creators, entrepreneurs and innovators belong. You don’t follow trends, you set them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About NeueHouse Madison Square&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located in the heart of the Flatiron District, NeueHouse Madison Square is a landmark of New York’s creative scene, housed in a historic 1913 industrial building that once served as an auction house. NeueHouse Madison Square offers a timeless design, emotive experiences, and elevated hospitality.&amp;nbsp; Across eight floors, it offers special event spaces, membership lounges, private office suites, and a members-only restaurant and bar, all artfully blending an edgy, industrial aesthetic with the comfort and warmth of a designer residence.&lt;/p&gt;
