&lt;li&gt;Act as the cultural steward ensuring every activation is executed with precision and hospitality synonymous with both the brand and elevated hospitality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recruit, mentor, and develop a high-performing team, fostering a culture of excellence, collaboration, and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
