&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Catering &amp;amp; Event Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Support the execution of catering orders for meetings and large-scale events. This includes meticulous prep, timely transport, and the precise assembly of banquet-style menus with a focus on punctuality and temperature control.&lt;/li&gt;
