&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Standard Bearer:&lt;/strong&gt; Follow all NeueHouse steps of service and maintain rigorous standards for sanitation, organization, and food handling across both the restaurant line and event kitchens.&lt;/li&gt;
